<l>īroṟṟut toṭarmoḻi yiṭaittoṭa rākā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are only twice three (kinds of words) where <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> shortens :</l>
<l rend="space">the <foreign xml:lang="ta">īreḻuttorumoḻi</foreign> or the ' two-letter words ',</l>
<l>the <foreign xml:lang="ta">uyirttoṭar(moḻi)</foreign> or the ' vowel-sequence words ',</l>
<l>the <foreign xml:lang="ta">iṭaittoṭar(moḻi)</foreign> or the ' semivowel-sequence words '</l>
<l>the <foreign xml:lang="ta">āytattoṭarmoḻi</foreign> or the ' āytam-sequence words ',</l>
<l>the <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṉṟoṭar(moḻi)</foreign> or the ' voiceless stop-sequence words ',</l>
<l>[and] the <foreign xml:lang="ta">meṉṟoṭar(moḻi)</foreign> or the ' nasal-sequence words '.</l>
      </lg>
